Requirements
************

   The following packages from Geek Gadgets are required to be
installed.

   * ixemul.library version 45.1 or newer

   * groff - to format man pages in nroff format

   * less - the default pager

   * perl - for @{b}catman.pl@{ub} and @{b}makewhatis.pl@{ub}

   * gzip - to process compressed man pages

   It is also assumed that a set of standard Unix utilities like cat,cp,
sh, sort etc. are available. They can be found in the GNU fileutils,
GNU textutils, GNU sh-utils, and pdksh packages.


@endnode

